For typical Safe user support queries, use our dedicated Intercom service. You can access it via the chat icon on:

Help Center - https://help.safe.global/
Safe Web - https://app.safe.global/
Safe iOS Mobile - https://apps.apple.com/app/id1515759131

Please be polite and respect the @Serv.eth team, they're our trusted partners for assisting with user support queries. Only those with the @Safe Team team or @Serv.eth support role should be trusted for DMs
